Package optimizer

Class PipeCost

  • java.lang.Object
    • optimizer.PipeCost
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<PipeCost>
    public class PipeCost
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<PipeCost>
    The PipeCost class represents the cost information for a commercial pipe. It implements the Comparable interface to allow for comparison based on maximum pressure and diameter.
